## 3 - Faculty Leave Management System

The Faculty Leave Management System is developed as a capstone project to
simplify and automate the process of managing faculty leave in educational institutions.
The system provides an online platform where faculty members can apply for leave and
administrators can review, approve, or reject the requests efficiently. It helps in
maintaining proper records of faculty leaves, reduces manual paperwork, and improves
communication between staff and management. The system also allows easy tracking of
leave status and generates reports for better management.

